productReviews.reviewText: It only works when I'm New Caledonia.
My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
heard about this on gypsy jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
I tried to attack it but got meatball all over it.
one of my hobbies is baking. and when i'm baking this works great.
